      <title>总统们穿梭于纽约创造了鲜明的分屏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/biden-trump-in-new-york-create-stark-split-screen-with-columbia-protests-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，总统乔·拜登和唐纳德·特朗普在曼哈顿相距仅几英里，但背景却十分鲜明：共和党预定的候选人坐在昏暗的法庭里，而现任总司令则与纽约市的精英一起参加筹款活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/biden-trump-in-new-york-create-stark-split-screen-with-columbia-protests-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 16:18:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
